OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,FJersey charity shops in St Helier say
OL,7,Fthat thefts are becoming a daily
OL,8,Foccurrence, undermining their
OL,9,Ffundraising.
OL,11,FElk Hargreaves, general manager of the
OL,12,FCare and Relief for the Young shop,
OL,13,Ftold ITV News that she thinks some
OL,14,Fislanders see the store as an easy
OL,15,Ftarget.
OL,17,FShe says that many volunteers who run
OL,18,Fthe shop are elderly and are not
OL,19,Ftrained to deal with shoplifters.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779451870
OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,FElk adds that while only "one or two"
OL,7,Fitems are taken every day, it has a
OL,8,Fknock-on impact on the charity.
OL,10,F"The intention is that the money will
OL,11,Fgo toward our children's projects, and
OL,12,Fso we lose that opportunity when
OL,13,Fpeople take things without paying, so
OL,14,Fthat's a shame as well."
OL,16,FCare and Relief for the Young is now
OL,17,Ftaking extra precautions to reduce the
OL,18,Famount of stolen items.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779451870
OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,FVideo surveillance is now used, with
OL,7,Fcertain lucrative items taken off
OL,8,Fdisplay, and branded products are
OL,9,Fbeing placed closer to the cashier's
OL,10,Fdesk.
OL,12,FDespite frustrations about the thefts,
OL,13,FElk is urging anyone who needs help to
OL,14,Fcome and speak to them rather than
OL,15,Fsteal
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779451870
OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,F"There are two elements to charity
OL,7,Fshops where we're trying to give
OL,8,Fpeople in Jersey an opportunity to
OL,9,Ffind low-price items for their home,
OL,10,Fand for themselves, and for their
OL,11,Ffamilies.
OL,13,F"I think sometimes people forget the
OL,14,Fother side of it, with the money going
OL,15,Fto our children's projects and the
OL,16,Fcauses that we support.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779451870
OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,F"We understand that it's difficult
OL,7,F(...) if you are struggling, then
OL,8,Fplease come and talk to us because
OL,9,Fwe're more than happy to support you
OL,10,Fand help in any way that we can."
OL,12,FClaire Mackenzie, from Jersey Hospice
OL,13,FCare, also said there is a "fair
OL,14,Fproblem" with theft in their shops,
OL,15,Feven with the introduction of CCTV and
OL,16,Fwarning signs to deter theft.
OL,18,FClaire told ITV News that witnessing a
OL,19,Ftheft can be "heartbreaking" for many
OL,20,Fvolunteers.
OL,26,@oD@ApmoD@Epn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779451870
OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,F"For those people to be going out of
OL,7,Ftheir way and ultimately giving us the
OL,8,Fgift of their time to be met with
OL,9,Fpeople that maybe don't have the same
OL,10,Fmotivations in life to support a
OL,11,Fcharity, it can be a heartbreaking
OL,12,Fexperience.
OL,14,F"You still see this sort of thing
OL,15,Fhappening in retail and commercial
OL,16,Fbackgrounds too so as much as it's a
OL,17,Fheartbreaking thing for us to have in
OL,18,Fcharity retail.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779451870
OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,FIt's not an exclusive problem in
OL,7,Fcharity, but I think there's perhaps a
OL,8,Fmisconception around what we'll then
OL,9,Fdo with it or that we won't put
OL,10,Fmeasures in place to protect our
OL,11,Fgoods."
OL,13,FSgt David Bowler, from the States of
OL,14,FJersey Police's Community Policing
OL,15,FTeam, is encouraging anyone working in
OL,16,Fa charity shop to report any thefts
OL,17,Fdirectly to officers.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779451870
OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,F"I would put a plea out today for
OL,7,Fthose shop owners who are experiencing
OL,8,Fshoplifting to make sure that they do
OL,9,Freport it to us," Sgt Bowler stated.
OL,11,F"The better understanding we have of
OL,12,Fthe issue, the more effectively we can
OL,13,Ftarget our resources to actually
OL,14,Freduce those issues."
OL,16,FHe added that the police want to work
OL,17,Fwith shops of all shapes and sizes to
OL,18,Freduce the likelihood of crime
OL,19,Fhappening.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779451870
OL,3,CThieves raiding charity shop becoming
OL,4,C'a daily occurence', charities say
OL,6,F"We will work with all shopkeepers to
OL,7,Fdeliver successful prosecutions and
OL,8,Fsend out a message and a deterrent to
OL,9,Fother people who are thinking of
OL,10,Fstealing."
OL,12,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,13,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,14,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,15,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,16,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,17,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,18,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,19,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,20,FThursday...
